name: Coruscant: Private Platform (Docking Bay)
LocationDStext: If deployed by your [Virtural Block 7] objective, may not be seperated from Palpatine's Quaters. Your docking bay transit to or from here is free.
LocationLStext: All docking bay transit from same site as Insidious Prisoner is free. Your docking bay transit to or from here requires 2 Force.
